00:13:36.810 --> 00:13:41.810 position:89%
It was one of the first African novels written in English

00:13:40.280 --> 00:13:45.280
to achieve national acclaim.

00:13:43.000 --> 00:13:48.000 position:59%
Set in the early days of colonization,

00:13:45.680 --> 00:13:50.680 position:98%
