00:13:58.970 --> 00:14:03.970
to adapt to the changing conditions

00:14:01.200 --> 00:14:06.200 position:58%
under imminent European colonization.

00:14:05.090 --> 00:14:10.090 position:98%
One of the first works of fiction to present African village life

00:14:08.940 --> 00:14:13.940 position:98%
from an African perspective, Things Fall Apart was published in 1958,

00:14:14.360 --> 00:14:19.360 position:97%
just two years before the end of the Century of British rule in Nigeria.

00:14:19.450 --> 00:14:24.450 position:98%
And of course we are celebrating it as has been mentioned, tonight,

00:14:22.650 --> 00:14:27.650 position:78%
the 50th anniversary of its publication this year.

00:14:27.790 --> 00:14:32.790 position:66%
